{"tid":1419051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃藝人變過街老鼠 《東方》報道 劉浩龍轟何韻詩「X樣」","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:13:41.000Z","uid":219147,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"73b9c29155480c3d3ffb44e5ad7f88a3043b2e02","tid":1419051,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ya95dAL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYa95dAL.png&h=cd7104e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩變成過街老鼠？！黃藝人何韻詩日前在天后容祖兒的Instagram留言，結果被容祖兒粉絲圍攻，叫佢咪連累人（請按此重溫）。據《東方日報》報道當中容祖兒前男友兼藝人劉浩龍更忍不住大鬧何韻詩是「X樣」。<br />\n<br />\n劉冷嘲：世界好多壞人<br />\n<br />\n劉浩龍在私人Instagram帳號中上載一張車尾照，當中的車牌是「MY JOEY」，在以帖文形式指「呢個世界好多壞人，例如何韻詩個X樣」。照片跟文字都顯然時指向何韻詩上綱上線的事件。帖文得到不少圈中人讚好，可見眾人在事件的取向。<br />\n<br />\n黃絲成日自詡代表民意，但次次出現都如過街老鼠咁被趕走。點解會咁？唔該佢哋自己好好諗吓！<br />\n<br />\n原圖：劉浩龍 Facebook Page、何韻詩 Facebook Page<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WilfredLau.seehing/photos/a.128169577239748/1925218340868187/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWilfredLau.seehing%2Fphotos%2Fa.128169577239748%2F1925218340868187%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=a3e1cdca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WilfredLau.seehing/photos/a.128169577239748/1925218340868187/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HOCCHOCC/photos/a.242914560229/10161981172520230/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHOCCHOCC%2Fphotos%2Fa.242914560229%2F10161981172520230%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=6b02192e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HOCCHOCC/photos/a.242914560229/10161981172520230/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n黃絲被Joey藍絲軍粉團圍巢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4361672db49a53655b50c35f9333584aa8105fff","tid":1419051,"uid":219147,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8z8mwpn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8z8mwpn.png&h=9835889e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"267fe6a47153fb01acb7051c34b25cb14ca9b1c5","tid":1419051,"uid":196924,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:32:44.000Z","msg":"容姨除咗自己班所謂歌迷咪又係神憎鬼厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文匯之友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵埋搵埋咁多，發財都唔識立品<br />\n做一世楊受成肉便器啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab0d4d089d72305c193d3fc9e55751829be7c87","tid":1419051,"uid":22558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:46:10.000Z","msg":"都唔知邊個先係過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea04c8109299d640949f75e5e112b92d2da5926","tid":1419051,"uid":219147,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"267fe6a47153fb01acb7051c34b25cb14ca9b1c5","tid":1419051,"uid":196924,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:32:44.000Z","msg":"容姨除咗自己班所謂歌迷咪又係神憎鬼厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文匯之友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵埋搵埋咁多，發財都唔識立品<br />\n做一世楊受成肉便器啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:13:41.000Z","msg":"英皇娛樂咪又係勾結黑社會 揾自己友係背後撐祖姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}